{"tid":584804,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"諗整都唔明，點解唔可以立法禁煙草？","createTime":"2018-03-08T05:54:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-08T07:04:16.000Z","uid":166064,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"86e161e2f5c2e3ef42554aa3893ce9b78e4398fe","tid":584804,"uid":166064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T05:54:56.000Z","msg":"就係因為稅收高？<br />\n明明政府都要又賣廣告又印煙盒同人講吸煙會死會陽痿<br />\n明知對人體好有害，又二手煙影響到人，又空氣污染又臭<br />\n點解唔可以禁咗佢？<br />\n點解毒品又要禁？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你食還食自己暱埋食囉，又要邊行邊食噴曬啲煙過嚟</span></span>"},{"pid":"bd205cf37827f94af00166b2e754f52b47fec966","tid":584804,"uid":166064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T05:55:25.000Z","msg":"諗極<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自膠"},{"pid":"d055e2224759a294ced08f404713795fbdec9258","tid":584804,"uid":16871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T05:56:33.000Z","msg":"無錯就係因為稅收高"},{"pid":"332cf6378ee0132750cf1a66f70544879bf4e54c","tid":584804,"uid":5159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T05:56:53.000Z","msg":"$"},{"pid":"728e7cd3dcd912e30526b26bde0357d3ed700084","tid":584804,"uid":41846,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T05:59:09.000Z","msg":"人權問題掛<br />\n同埋應該會違反香港嘅自由貿易原則<br />\n所以祗可以加稅"},{"pid":"ebba48b0498fffe071220e7db346884d1b888335","tid":584804,"uid":135306,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T06:00:04.000Z","msg":"因為已經太多人食 你完全禁煙會有好多人反你 <br />\n仲有同毒品唔同 普遍社會對佢既觀感冇咁差<br />\n所以立法個時應該會好多阻礙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申: 支持對煙剷趕盡殺絕"},{"pid":"fefb0a79d53aad3af996ed7df7a97513436ce611","tid":584804,"uid":56157,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T06:01:00.000Z","msg":"因為賣煙草個班會反對。"},{"pid":"7318691190c9593b5b3d3cc2a371700ae5f1f3eb","tid":584804,"uid":12853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T06:01:38.000Z","msg":"因為$"},{"pid":"54f0ffad9c522ccf158753eef54d3af752e6fff4","tid":584804,"uid":86125,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T06:04:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"57f9242b387dacfbf2584bc516f0ae589282de07","tid":584804,"uid":107927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T06:05:22.000Z","msg":"其實係部份煙民的&quot;公德心&quot;問題<br />\n多過煙本身的問題"},{"pid":"2df3382e368ec0a328f1bbdb806abad973993b8b","tid":584804,"uid":57554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T06:07:20.000Z","msg":"2010年全年煙草稅總收入為38億。<br />\n<br />\n假設呢八年都係咁上下，其實個收入對政府黎講，唔算係特別高。相反，呢到收左38億，另外一隻手要比錢搞控煙辦，要搵人捉人掉煙頭，醫療又係錢。<br />\n<br />\n所以應該就唔關錢事，關社會風氣同習慣事。"},{"pid":"d476e36661af7e00221d9268ec96b28137588dc1","tid":584804,"uid":51760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T06:48:04.000Z","msg":"係政府既角度黎講<br />\n啲人食煙會危害健康 縮短壽命<br />\n政府可以養少你幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 社會學jj"},{"pid":"9f60a216998f11c9e478a73f4224a7e6aa107b7b","tid":584804,"uid":90180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T06:51:31.000Z","msg":"可以減輕人口老化，減少福利開支"},{"pid":"afb0d12e8c288504e5107fe2e6a443b0cf12fb7a","tid":584804,"uid":16756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T06:52:02.000Z","msg":"又唔見禁酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b241e1788b96b3717100c209f5272969de518ef","tid":584804,"uid":15880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d476e36661af7e00221d9268ec96b28137588dc1","tid":584804,"uid":51760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T06:48:04.000Z","msg":"係政府既角度黎講<br />\n啲人食煙會危害健康 縮短壽命<br />\n政府可以養少你幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 社